ter&#39;,&#39;Arial&#39;;font-size:17px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;=
line-height:150%;text-align:left;mso-line-height-alt:25.5px;"><p style=3D"m=
argin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">How in the name of Bubbles the Chimp did this h=
appen? After all,
per three sources involved with the project, Branca assured King and the fi=
lmmakers that there was nothing to worry about, no skeletons in Michael=E2=
=80=99s closet that weren=E2=80=99t already known, and no surprises that wo=
uld put the film or its narrative in jeopardy. It <em>is</em> well known th=
at Branca was in and out of Jackson=E2=80=99s life in the late =E2=80=9980s=
 and early =E2=80=9990s, returning right around the time of the Chandler si=
tuation. So it would have made sense that Cochran, the late litigator, and =
not Branca,
would have handled the settlement with the family. But still, Branca is the=
 co-executor of an estate worth billions, so the buck stops with him.=C2=A0=
</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0=
;margin-bottom:0px;">The catalyst for all this was a September <a href=3D"h=
ttps://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1lEQUt2UktxclJLZ0dVbHI3=
TmxFeFJyZ1QzdFNQWVZ6ND0iLCJocmVmIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZnQuY29tL2NvbnRlbnQvZDg=
2MjQ4YTAtOGQ4Zi00MjY5LWJjMTQtYjRlMzMwYWRhMjY4P3V0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1XaGF0K0klMj=
dtK0hlYXJpbmcrLStTVUJTQ1JJQkVSUyslMjgxJTJGMjMlMkYyNSUyOVx1MDAyNnV0bV9jb250Z=
W50PVdoYXQrSSUyN20rSGVhcmluZystK1NVQlNDUklCRVJTKyUyODElMkYyMyUyRjI1JTI5XHUw=
MDI2dXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbF9hY3Rpb25cdTAwMjZ1dG1fc291cmNlPWN1c3RvbWVyLmlvXHU=
wMDI2dXRtX3Rlcm09ZjZjNjA2MTdkYTQyYWJkMTJhIiwiaW50ZXJuYWwiOiJmNmM2MDYxN2RhND=
JhYmQxMmEiLCJsaW5rX2lkIjoyMDU0MTQxfQ/134d1cfdafa2bd5d3c886dc83bf0fe5c1ed611=
586769da0f0bb3703be09c3946" style=3D"text-decoration:underline;color:#d4000=
0;">story</a> in the <em>Financial Times</em> that revealed Branca had made=
 secret hush money
payments to five accusers who had come forward after HBO aired the 2019 doc=
umentary <em>Leaving Neverland</em>, which focused on accusers <strong>Wade=
 Robson</strong> and <strong>James Safechuck</strong>. According to the <em=
>FT</em>, these new accusers threatened to go public with claims that Jacks=
on had acted inappropriately, and the estate agreed to collectively pay the=
m $16.5 million to stay quiet. Then last year, as the payments neared their=
 end, one of the five accusers allegedly violated
the agreement, seeking an additional <em>$213 million</em>, so the estate b=
rought an arbitration claim against him.</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bot=
tom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">When the <em>F=
T</em> found out about the payments, so did the <em>Michael</em> filmmakers=
 and their studio partners, who didn=E2=80=99t love being blindsided. <em>W=
hat else has the estate not revealed?</em> Everyone involved knows this mov=
ie will have a giant target on it when it=E2=80=99s released. Michael
Jackson has always been a magnet for crazy people and <em>litigious </em>cr=
azy people. Everything about <em>Michael</em> needs to be airtight, and the=
 filmmakers feared that any =E2=80=9Cnoise=E2=80=9D around Jackson from new=
 accusers could damage the film=E2=80=99s reception. The estate is already =
battling in court against Robson and Safechuck, although a planned trial ea=
rly this year has been delayed until 2026.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;ma=
rgin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;">But that was just the
beginning. According to two sources, around the time he revealed the hush m=
oney payments, Branca let the filmmakers know that there was a legal issue =
with the third act of the movie. That=E2=80=99s when everyone learned about=
 the decades-old deal with the Chandlers. Mind you, this was <em>after</em>=
 shooting had wrapped on a film with a $150 million budget. It was <em>afte=
r</em> King had teased footage of the movie at CinemaCon last April, and Fu=
qua had gone to ComicCon in July to tell everyone how
great it was turning out. I can only imagine how the famously emotional Kin=
g reacted. If <em>Michael</em> now can=E2=80=99t =E2=80=9Cdramatize=E2=80=
=9D the Chandler claims, which are the backbone of the film, what, exactly,=
 will the third act entail?=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0</p></div>
</td></tr></tbody></table>
</td></tr></tbody></table>
</td></tr></tbody></table>
